Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ　吉野って　割とよくね？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think Yoshino's cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:45.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあね。\N真広いなけりゃ　ただの人だし。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But without Mahiro around, he's just another guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:48.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪顔はいいんだし\Nとりあえず　いっとけば？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so fine. Why don't you go for it?
